Interface ITxnCommitEntityEventInterceptor<E extends AuditEvent,F extends ITxnCommitEntityAuditEventFilter>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - event class (events to be filtered)
    F - filter class (filter to apply)
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ITxnCommitEntityEventInterceptor<E extends AuditEvent,F extends ITxnCommitEntityAuditEventFilter>
    This interface represents an interceptor for an entity transaction commit phase.
